headline: 3 Brilliant Growth Stocks to Buy Now and Hold for the Long Term
summary: If a business demonstrates consistent increases in profits and free cash flow, the market will naturally bid up its share price and make it more valuable over time.  Here are three such growth stocks that you can consider owning for the long term.  Ecolab (NYSE: ECL) specializes in water treatment technology, providing hygiene and infection-prevention solutions to customers in more than 170 countries.
